citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at1:30 pm on 01-NOV-
23. USDA was able to make contact by phone. The licensee stated he is no longer conducting regulated activity and
would like to cancel his license.
Written notification should be sent to the main office at the address below or by email. Please include your customer
number and license number.
USDA, APHIS, AC
Building B, Mailstop #3W11
2150 Centre Avenue
Fort Collins, CO 80526--8117
email to: animalcare@usda.gov
End Section
